            "en": "The cost of an AI chatbot implementation varies according to the complexity of the use cases, the expected volume of conversations, and the level of integration with your existing tools (CRM, ERP, messaging). For an SME, solutions range from a few hundred euros per month for turnkey SaaS tools to several thousand for custom developments. Step UpAI offers free audits to identify the solution best suited to your budget and specific objectives."
